      "comment": "SWEET IDEAL (12) finds a suitable assignment to resume in after tackling some good company at the end of her last campaign. Tricky draw but races well both here and at the distance and was readied with a trial win. KOSIMO (9) settled back from a similar draw last start then made up a stack of ground to score by a nose, his second win at this venue from his past four outings. Big chance again. REPELLING (3) hasn't done a bad job to come from wider barriers and finish fourth in his last two outings here. Contender from the favourable draw. ALWAYS BE BLAKEY (11) was midfield from the back row last time but had recorded a string of wins and placing prior and is suited returning to a venue where his record is strong.",
